# Local Claude notes for Stashd

Copy this file to `CLAUDE.local.md` if you need machine-specific notes.

Do not commit `CLAUDE.local.md`.

## Local paths

```text
Repo: /path/to/stashd
Media scratch: /path/to/stashd/media
Data scratch: /path/to/stashd/data
```

## Local commands

```bash
composer lint
composer test
composer test:feature
composer test:docker-smoke:no-build
```

## Local cautions

- Do not run live provider/download tests unless explicitly asked.
- Do not use real provider credentials in prompts or logs.
- Do not paste raw podcast feed URLs containing tokens into chat.
